Type: Package
Package: kfre
Title: KFRE Risk Prediction Tools (R)
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    c(person("Leonid", "Shpaner",
             email = "lshpaner@ucla.edu",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             comment = c(
               ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0009-0007-5311-8095",
               URL   = "https://leonshpaner.com"
             )))
Description: Implements the Kidney Failure Risk Equation (KFRE; Tangri et
    al.)  to compute 2- and 5-year kidney failure risk (4-, 6-, and
    8-variable models), append risk columns to data frames, classify CKD
    stages and ESRD outcomes, and evaluate and plot model performance.
